OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,C'proceed cautiously', says minister
OL,6,FTrials of the Army's troubled Ajax
OL,7,Farmoured vehicle will go ahead, a
OL,8,Fdefence minister has said.
OL,10,FIn a written statement published on
OL,11,FTuesday, Luke Pollard said the
OL,12,Fprogramme will be "proceeding
OL,13,Fcautiously" after use of the vehicle
OL,14,Fwas halted last year.
OL,16,FThe decision to stop using the Ajax
OL,17,Fcame after soldiers became unwell from
OL,18,Fnoise and vibration during a training
OL,19,Fexercise in November.
OL,26,@tD@SOUuD@KO]
