OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777493189
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,C'proceed cautiously', says minister
OL,6,FThis came weeks after Mr Pollard said
OL,7,Fthe #6.3 billion programme had "left
OL,8,Fits troubles behind", declaring the
OL,9,Fvehicle manufactured by General
OL,10,FDynamics in Merthyr Tydfil, South
OL,11,FWales, was ready to be deployed on
OL,12,Foperations.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, Mr Pollard said an
OL,15,Finvestigation found "a combination of
OL,16,Ffactors" was likely to have caused the
OL,17,Fsymptoms reported by soldiers,
OL,18,Fincluding technical issues,
OL,19,Fvariability in training and
OL,20,Fexperience, cold exposure and air
OL,21,Fquality in the Ajax.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@TO]wD@UOUxD@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777493189
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,C'proceed cautiously', says minister
OL,6,FHe said all personnel who reported
OL,7,Fissues in November, during Exercise
OL,8,FTitan Storm in Hampshire, have
OL,9,Freturned to normal duties and the
OL,10,Fmajority suffered from "temporary
OL,11,Fsymptoms".
OL,13,FHe said: "I have now agreed to restart
OL,14,Fthe acceptance of vehicles from
OL,15,F(manufacturer) General Dynamics.
OL,16,FHowever, I accept that the experience
OL,17,Ffor our soldiers using Ajax has not
OL,18,Fbeen good enough and that is not
OL,19,Facceptable.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@IO]uD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777493189
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,C'proceed cautiously', says minister
OL,6,F"I have implemented strict new
OL,7,Fcontrols on the reintroduction of the
OL,8,FAjax vehicles that is focused on
OL,9,Fproviding a significantly improved
OL,10,Fuser experience.
OL,12,F"We have been engaging extensively and
OL,13,Fdirectly with our soldiers throughout
OL,14,Fthis process ` their experiences
OL,15,Fmatter and they are shaping much of
OL,16,Fwhat we do next.
OL,18,F"As a result, we are considering a
OL,19,Fphased approach to restarting the Ajax
OL,20,Fprogramme."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
