PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777493189
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,C'proceed cautiously', says minister
OL,6,FThe first phase will include the
OL,7,Frestarting of trials with a limited
OL,8,Fnumber of vehicles and under "very
OL,9,Fcontrolled circumstances", he said.
OL,11,FThe Ajax programme, which was
OL,12,Foriginally intended to enter service
OL,13,Fin 2017, has suffered long delays
OL,14,Fbecause noise and vibration injured
OL,15,Fsoldiers who tested the vehicles.
OL,17,F"While we are proceeding cautiously
OL,18,Fwith Ajax, we know we have more to do
OL,19,Fto rebuild confidence in the vehicle,
OL,20,Fand we do not underestimate the work
OL,21,Fstill ahead," Mr Pollard added.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@YO]yD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
