OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777493189
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,C'proceed cautiously', says minister
OL,6,F"We aspire to deliver a vehicle into
OL,7,Fservice that is effective on the
OL,8,Fbattlefield and works for our
OL,9,Fsoldiers."
OL,11,FA spokesman for General Dynamics in
OL,12,FMerthyr Tydfil said: "GD UK welcomes
OL,13,Fthe conclusions of the Army Safety
OL,14,FInvestigation Team and the decision by
OL,15,Fthe Ministry of Defence to resume
OL,16,Facceptance and operation of Ajax
OL,17,Fvehicles under a phased and carefully
OL,18,Fcontrolled approach, focused on
OL,19,Fdelivering a significantly improved
OL,20,Fuser experience for soldiers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@VOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
