PN,46907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777493189
OL,3,CAjax armoured vehicle programme to
OL,4,C'proceed cautiously', says minister
OL,6,F"The safety of soldiers is, and has
OL,7,Falways been, our highest priority.
OL,9,F"GD UK has confidence in the
OL,10,Fperformance and protection Ajax is
OL,11,Fdesigned to provide. It is the world's
OL,12,Fmost advanced, fully digitised,
OL,13,Farmoured fighting vehicle and ensures
OL,14,Fsoldiers see and understand the
OL,15,Fbattlefield faster than any adversary."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOU
